              "free_text": [
                " This article, by A.J.Cox and",
                "        D.Crumpton, gives (n,2n) cross-sections for",
                "        the Cu isotopes one of which, Cu-63(n,2n) is",
                "        superseded in the present work in which",
                "        more recent branching ratio is used. The",
                "        theoretical treatment is also reproduced."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "AUTHOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
